snippet.title: 'Midnight Scenes: The Highway' Trailer. A short game by Octavi Navarro
snippet.description:
I made a short adventure game! :D
GET IT NOW 
On itch.io:
https://octavinavarro.itch.io/midnight-scenes-the-highway
On Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1279700/Midnight_Scenes_The_Highway/
On GOG:
https://www.gog.com/en/game/midnight_scenes_the_highway_special_edition

I hope you enjoy it!! :)
